'''Algeria''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was added to Bitlife in the May 10, 2020 update, alongside [[Bangladesh]], [[Bolivia]], [[Croatia]], [[Georgia]], [[Hungary]], [[Jordan]], [[Qatar]], [[Slovakia]], and [[Zimbabwe]]. Its default cities are the capital, Algiers, along with Oran.

== Vital Statistics ==
Currency:  USD ($)

Default Cities: Algiers, Oran

Graduation Age:  18

Minimum Age to Drop out of School:  17

Free University:  No

Minimum Legal Driving Age:  18

Same-Sex Dating Legal:  No

Same-Sex Marriage Legal: No

Changing Last Name After Marriage Permitted: No

Free Healthcare: No

Gambling Legal: No

Death Penalty Legal: Yes

Conjugal Visits Permitted: No

Commercial Surrogacy Legal: Yes

